@startuml
title Categorization Review Human-in-the-Loop Flow

actor Analyst
participant "finance_tooling CLI" as CLI
database "transactions_normalized.csv" as NORMALIZED
participant "transactions_review.xlsx" as REVIEW <<file>>
database "transaction_overrides.yaml" as TX_OVERRIDES
database "review_state.parquet" as REVIEW_STATE
participant "transform stage" as TRANSFORM

group Review Export
Analyst -> CLI: review-export\n[with flags OR defaults]
alt flags omitted
CLI -> CLI: Resolve defaults from .env\nFINANCE_PROCESSED_PATH
end
CLI -> NORMALIZED: Read normalized table
CLI -> REVIEW_STATE: Load persisted review state
CLI -> REVIEW: Write uncategorized review rows\n(default) or all rows with --include-categorized
CLI --> Analyst: Export summary\n(row count + output path)
end

group Manual Review
Analyst -> REVIEW: Edit category/subcategory,\nproject_tags, reviewed, review_comment
note right of Analyst
Keep key fields stable:
- transaction_id
- description
- bank
- account_label

Use:
- category/subcategory for manual transaction corrections
- project_tags for manual project tagging
- reviewed for progress tracking
- review_comment for analyst notes
end note
end

group Review Import
Analyst -> CLI: review-import\n[with flags OR defaults]
alt flags omitted
CLI -> CLI: Resolve defaults from .env\n(processed + transaction override paths)
end
CLI -> TX_OVERRIDES: Load existing transaction overrides
CLI -> REVIEW_STATE: Load existing review state
CLI -> REVIEW: Read reviewed rows
CLI -> CLI: Validate rows + build transaction-level changes
alt dry-run enabled
CLI --> Analyst: Preview upsert counters\n(no file write)
else apply import
CLI -> TX_OVERRIDES: Backup existing file
CLI -> TX_OVERRIDES: Upsert transaction overrides and write file
CLI -> REVIEW_STATE: Upsert review state and write file
CLI --> Analyst: Import summary\n(updated/inserted/skipped)
end
end

group Apply New Overrides
Analyst -> TRANSFORM: Run transform\nor review-import --run-transform
TRANSFORM -> TX_OVERRIDES: Load updated overrides
TRANSFORM -> REVIEW_STATE: Load review markers
TRANSFORM --> Analyst: New categorized outputs\nwith reviewed projected into normalized output
end

@enduml
